4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed to fast-track individuals into cybersecurity roles, requiring no prior knowledge. The program provides a comprehensive foundation in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, while emphasizing cloud security, penetration testing, and threat intelligence analysis. The bootcamp includes 16 weeks of training with three live online classes per week, limited to 16 participants, ensuring a focused learning environment. Graduates receive an official completion certificate. The syllabus is available in English and Spanish, with live classes tailored to the campus language. For more details, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop